trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator.ItemsChanged> event is raised by an <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator> to inform layouts that the items collection has changed.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator.ItemsChanged>händelse utlöses av en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator>att informera layouter items-mängden har ändrats.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.IItemContainerGenerator> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator.ItemsChanged>

trans-unit.source: Gets the action that occurred on the items collection.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar den åtgärd som inträffat på objektmängden.

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of items that were involved in the change.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar antalet objekt som var inblandade i ändringen.

trans-unit.source: Integer that represents the number of items involved in the change.
trans-unit.target: Heltal som representerar antalet objekt som ingår i ändringen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)] elements involved in the change.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar antalet [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)] element som är involverad i ändringen.

trans-unit.source: Integer that represents the number of UI elements involved in the change.
trans-unit.target: Heltal som representerar antalet UI-element som ingår i ändringen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the position in the collection before the change occurred.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar position i samlingen innan ändringen utfördes.

trans-unit.source: Gets the position in the collection where the change occurred.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar position i samlingen där ändringen utfördes.
